i. De standarder vi har satt i Norge skal gjelde for barn som befinner seg i Norge. Barn her skal ha en trygg oppvekst, uten frykt for vold og overgrep."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3ef1d002397baca1617cb803b96518bd47d7b1a4b2705d548fb7aee2029834a6"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-22T21:27:36.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- Den mest alvorlige saken jeg har v\u00e6rt borti, sier kontrollkomiteens leder, Rolf Jarle Br\u00f8ske."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12102689.ece/t85arn/ALTERNATES/w980-default/jarle.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/195a83d1eb30cb7ea28f05fd30bc1437f13733f4.jpg?5989f74a"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Slo alarm om bortf\u00f8rte barn -adressa.no", "La vekk alt annet", "- Flere kan forsvinne"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "195a83d1eb30cb7ea28f05fd30bc1437f13733f4"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["forsvunnede barn", "slo alarm", "sak", "bortf\u00f8rte barn", "barn"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["barne", "per olav nilsen", "adresseavisen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["norge", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["rune ols\u00f8", "rita ottervik", "rolf jarle br\u00f8ske", "gunn r\u00f8stad"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["pluss", "pluss/nyheter"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming